The paper proposes a new algorithm for sampling from a determinantal point process, which has applications in machine learning, stochastic optimization, data summarization, and low-rank matrix reconstruction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
